data.description: *WOW* Seller is offering $10,000 in concessions with a full price offer to be used for rate buy down or closing costs.  Check out this beautiful two-story, three bedroom home in Northeast Crossing.  Enter into the serene living room that opens up beautifully to the clean, white kitchen. The main floor presents a functional living and dining space.  The master bedroom and bathroom offer a spa-like experience complete with double vanity, large walk-in closet, and clean lines. Upstairs a generous loft space creates an opportunity for a playroom, media room, or office. There are two other bedrooms and guest bathroom upstairs.  Carpet has been replaced since pictures were taken.  Just a short 15 minutes drive from Ft. Sam Houston and Joint Base SA.
